+{"id":"ids_ml_new-br4g.15","title":"Mirror console and ops tests to the new domain layout","description":"Mirror console and ops tests to the new domain layout.\n\nWhat:\n- Move console tests under tests/console and ops tests under tests/ops.\n- Make scope explicit where it matters and update imports to target canonical ids.console and ids.ops modules.\n- Keep runtime/core and ML test migration in their own beads.\n\nContext from Planning:\n- D6 requires mirrored ownership plus visible scope.\n- This bead isolates operator-facing tests so they do not compete with runtime or ML suite work.\n\nInstitutional Learnings:\n- Operator service and orchestration tests should follow the product seam they protect.\n\nFile scope:\n- tests/console/**\n- tests/ops/**\n- console/ops pytest support adjustments only if needed\n\nAcceptance:\n- Console and ops tests mirror the new domain layout.\n- Canonical imports are primary for console and ops tests.\n- Scope markers are explicit where relevant.\n\nVerify:\n- python -m pytest tests/console tests/ops -q\n\nValidated constraints:\n- Rely on the shared tests/conftest.py bootstrap before moving console or ops tests deeper.\n- Move console and ops tests as one domain slice aligned with their code-move beads.\n- Keep canonical ids.console and ids.ops imports primary after relocation.","status":"closed","priority":1,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-03-30T15:29:57.684754400Z","created_by":"QuietRiver","updated_at":"2026-03-30T19:00:31.564142800Z","closed_at":"2026-03-30T19:00:31.562430100Z","close_reason":"Completed: move console and ops tests into tests/console and tests/ops","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"labels":["high-risk","pytest","tests"],"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"ids_ml_new-br4g.15","depends_on_id":"ids_ml_new-br4g","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-03-30T15:29:57.684754400Z","created_by":"QuietRiver","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"ids_ml_new-br4g.15","depends_on_id":"ids_