+{"id":"ids_ml_new-br4g.16","title":"Mirror ML workflow tests to the new domain layout","description":"Mirror ML workflow tests to the new domain layout.\n\nWhat:\n- Move benchmark, training, and packaging related tests under tests/ml.\n- Keep imports aligned with canonical ml_pipeline modules.\n- Leave product-path test migration to the runtime/core and console/ops beads.\n\nContext from Planning:\n- D6 applies to the experiment/history zone as well.\n- This bead keeps ML test movement separate from production-path test movement.\n\nInstitutional Learnings:\n- Workflow tests should follow the pipeline they validate, not the historical flat script layout.\n\nFile scope:\n- tests/ml/**\n- ML pytest support adjustments only if needed\n\nAcceptance:\n- ML workflow tests live under tests/ml with clear scope markers when relevant.\n- Canonical ml_pipeline imports are primary.\n\nVerify:\n- python -m pytest tests/ml -q\n\nValidated constraints:\n- Reuse the shared tests/conftest.py bootstrap instead of copying per-file path hacks.\n- Move ML tests as one domain slice aligned with ml_pipeline moves.\n- Switch relocated tests to canonical ml_pipeline imports in the same change.","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-03-30T15:29:58.266792200Z","created_by":"QuietRiver","updated_at":"2026-03-30T18:40:17.959472700Z","closed_at":"2026-03-30T18:40:17.957922Z","close_reason":"Completed: moved ML workflow tests under tests/ml with shared bootstrap and canonical ml_pipeline imports","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"labels":["ml","pytest","tests"],"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"ids_ml_new-br4g.16","depends_on_id":"ids_ml_new-br4g","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-03-30T15:29:58.266792200Z","created_by":"QuietRiver","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"ids_ml_new-br4g.16","depends_on_id":"ids_ml_new-br4g.14","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-03-30T15:31:32.186611400Z","created_by":"QuietRiver","metadata":"{}","th