+{"id":"ids_ml_new-br4g.17","title":"Repoint domain documents into docs/current and docs/archive","description":"Repoint runtime, console, ops, and ML documents into the new current docs structure.\n\nWhat:\n- Move or rewrite active domain documents so they land under the docs/current navigation spine.\n- Archive superseded historical documents under docs/archive where appropriate.\n- Keep top-level navigation work in the earlier docs spine bead.\n\nContext from Planning:\n- D7 requires current and archived material to be visibly distinct.\n- This bead updates domain docs after the target package map is clear.\n\nInstitutional Learnings:\n- Active runbooks and architecture docs must mirror the real ownership seams.\n\nFile scope:\n- docs/current/runtime/**\n- docs/current/console/**\n- docs/current/operations/**\n- docs/current/ml/**\n- corresponding archived docs under docs/archive/**\n\nAcceptance:\n- Active runtime, console, ops, and ML docs live under docs/current.\n- Superseded material is archived instead of left mixed beside current docs.\n- README and current-doc paths point at the domain homes created by this bead.\n\nVerify:\n- Test-Path docs/current/runtime\n- Test-Path docs/current/console\n- Test-Path docs/current/operations\n- Test-Path docs/current/ml\n- rg -n docs/current/runtime README.md\n- rg -n docs/current/console README.md\n- rg -n docs/current/operations README.md\n- rg -n docs/current/ml README.md","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-03-30T15:29:58.894555900Z","created_by":"QuietRiver","updated_at":"2026-03-30T19:01:48.858268300Z","closed_at":"2026-03-30T19:01:48.856474400Z","close_reason":"Completed: repointed canonical docs under docs/current and archived superseded ML docs under docs/archive","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"labels":["docs","navigation","refactor"],"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"ids_ml_new-br4g.17","depends_on_id":"ids_ml_new-br4g","type":"parent-child","created_at":