 {"id":"ids_ml_new-mx1.1","title":"Resolve Review P2: Replace self-referential rollback oracle","description":"Problem: rollback regression test derives expected output from DEFAULT_STRUCTURED_RECORD_ADAPTER.adapt_record(...).to_record(), so the oracle depends on the implementation under test. Acceptance: replace the expected promoted output with an independent fixture or explicit expected record/value authored outside the production path.","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-03-28T01:38:29.970088900Z","created_by":"unknown","updated_at":"2026-03-28T01:42:42.707714200Z","closed_at":"2026-03-28T01:42:42.706309Z","close_reason":"Completed: replaced self-referential rollback oracle with fixture-authored expected record and locked rollback byte-preservation assertions","external_ref":"ids_ml_new-f4w::replace-self-referential-rollback-oracle-rerun-10","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"labels":["code_quality","rerun-10","review","review_p2"],"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"ids_ml_new-mx1.1","depends_on_id":"ids_ml_new-mx1","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-03-28T01:38:29.970088900Z","created_by":"unknown","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""}]}
