+- `HistGradientBoosting`: `12`
+
+## Cách ch?y ti?p
+
+### 1. Pilot run nhanh
+
+```powershell
+python F:\Work\IDS_ML_New\scripts\tune_top_models.py `
+  --models catboost,random_forest,hist_gb `
+  --trials catboost=4,random_forest=3,hist_gb=3 `
