+# Gói Model Cu?i Cůng
+
+## M?c tięu
+
+Model cu?i cůng không cňn lŕ t?p h?p file r?i r?c trong `artifacts`, mŕ lŕ m?t bundle có contract versioned d? runtime, preflight, vŕ operator workflow cůng d?c theo m?t chu?n duy nh?t.
+
+Script dóng gói:
+
+- [package_final_model.py](F:/Work/IDS_ML_New/scripts/package_final_model.py)
+
+Script inference vŕ dry-run:
+
+- [ids_inference.py](F:/Work/IDS_ML_New/scripts/ids_inference.py)
+
+Script qu?n lý promotion lifecycle:
+
+- [ids_model_bundle_manage.py](F:/Work/IDS_ML_New/scripts/ids_model_bundle_manage.py)
+
+## Bundle n?m ? dâu
+
+Bundle final hi?n t?i du?c dóng t?i:
+
+- `F:\Work\IDS_ML_New\artifacts\final_model\catboost_full_data_v1`
+
+Runtime production không d?c bundle b?ng cách tr? tay vŕo `model.cbm` hay `feature_columns.json`. Thay vŕo dó, live sensor d?c m?t activation record host-local, ví d?:
+
+- `/var/lib/ids-live-sensor/active_bundle.json`
+
+Activation record nŕy tr? t?i dúng m?t bundle dang active vŕ luu thęm metadata rollback v? bundle known-good tru?c dó.
+
+## Bundle g?m gě
+
+N?i dung bundle:
+
+- `model.cbm`
+- `feature_columns.json`
+- `model_bundle.json`
+- `metrics.json`
+- `training_summary.json`
+- `MODEL_CARD.md`
+
+## Ý nghia t?ng file
+
+### `model.cbm`
+
+Artifact mô hěnh `CatBoost full-data` dă du?c ch?t.
+
+### `feature_columns.json`
+
+Schema canonical c?a feature set mŕ inference contract hi?n t?i ch?p nh?n.
+
+### `model_bundle.json`
+
+Đây lŕ manifest versioned c?a bundle. T? `manifest_version = 2`, file nŕy lŕ production contract chính th?c cho:
+
+- v? trí model artifact
+- v? trí feature schema
+- threshold v?n hŕnh
+- nhăn `Attack/Benign`
+- provenance co b?n
+- compatibility metadata d? ch?ng minh bundle kh?p v?i feature schema vŕ inference contract hi?n t?i
+
+Compatibility block hi?n t?i khóa:
+
+- `feature_schema.kind = "feature_columns_json.v1"`
+- `inference_contract.version = "ids_binary_classifier.v1"`
+- `threshold_source = "bundle"`
+- không cho phép external override cho `model_path`, `feature_columns_path`, ho?c `threshold`
+
+Đi?u nŕy có nghia lŕ production runtime không du?c tr?n bundle A v?i schema ho?c threshold ngoŕi bundle.
+
+### `metrics.json`
+
+Tóm t?t metric cu?i cůng cho model card ho?c báo cáo nhanh.
+
+### `training_summary.json`
+
+Thông tin train full-data g?c.
+
+### `MODEL_CARD.md`
+
+Tŕi li?u mô t? model cu?i du?i d?ng ng?n g?n, d? tra c?u.
+
+## Cách d?ng l?i bundle
+
+```powershell
+python F:\Work\IDS_ML_New\scripts\package_final_model.py
+```
+
+Script nŕy s? emit `model_bundle.json` theo contract versioned hi?n t?i.
+
+## Cách verify vŕ důng bundle
+
+### 1. Verify candidate bundle
+
+```powershell
+python F:\Work\IDS_ML_New\scripts\ids_model_bundle_manage.py `
+  --activation-path F:\Work\IDS_ML_New\artifacts\runtime\active_bundle.json `
+  --json verify `
+  --bundle-root F:\Work\IDS_ML_New\artifacts\final_model\catboost_full_data_v1
+```
+
+L?nh nŕy ch? ki?m tra compatibility contract c?a candidate bundle. Nó không mutate tr?ng thái active.
+
+### 2. Dry-run inference tręn cůng host
+
+```powershell
+python F:\Work\IDS_ML_New\scripts\ids_inference.py `
+  --bundle-root F:\Work\IDS_ML_New\artifacts\final_model\catboost_full_data_v1 `
+  --input-path F:\Work\IDS_ML_New\artifacts\cic_iot_diad_2024_binary\clean\test.parquet `
+  --output-path F:\Work\IDS_ML_New\artifacts\demo\test_predictions_from_bundle.parquet `
+  --limit 1000
+```
+
+Đây lŕ same-host dry-run path hi?n t?i d? ki?m tra bundle m?i có th? load, align schema, vŕ score theo dúng inference contract tru?c khi promote.
+
+### 3. Promote bundle dă verify
+
+```powershell
+python F:\Work\IDS_ML_New\scripts\ids_model_bundle_manage.py `
+  --activation-path /var/lib/ids-live-sensor/active_bundle.json `
+  --json promote `
+  --bundle-root /opt/ids_ml_new/artifacts/final_model/catboost_full_data_v1
+```
+
+Promotion s? ghi l?i bundle active m?i b?ng atomic replace. N?u dă có bundle active tru?c dó, activation record cung luu `previous_bundle_*` d? rollback.
+
+### 4. Rollback v? known-good tru?c dó
+
+```powershell
+python F:\Work\IDS_ML_New\scripts\ids_model_bundle_manage.py `
+  --activation-path /var/lib/ids-live-sensor/active_bundle.json `
+  --json rollback
+```
+
+Rollback cung důng cůng activation contract vŕ cůng co ch? atomic replace. Không có copy-based fallback.
+
+## Vai trň c?a bundle trong realtime pipeline
+
+Bundle lŕ ngu?n c?u hěnh chu?n cho l?p realtime pre-model pipeline:
+
+- [ids_realtime_pipeline.py](F:/Work/IDS_ML_New/scripts/ids_realtime_pipeline.py)
+- [ids_realtime_pipeline_architecture.md](F:/Work/IDS_ML_New/docs/current/runtime/ids_realtime_pipeline_architecture.md)
+
+Trong pipeline hi?n t?i:
+
+- `feature_columns.json` lŕ contract c?a canonical model features
+- `model_bundle.json` gi? threshold, label names, vŕ compatibility metadata
+- `model.cbm` lŕ artifact scoring trung tâm
+- `active_bundle.json` lŕ entrypoint production duy nh?t d? runtime resolve bundle dang live
+
+L?p realtime ch? du?c phép důng bundle d?:
+
