+# Ki?n Trúc Realtime Pre-Model Pipeline Cho IDS
+
+## M?c tięu
+
+Tŕi li?u nŕy mô t? l?p runtime m?i n?m tru?c model IDS v1: nh?n `structured flow records` t? upstream extractor, ki?m tra record theo dúng contract `72` feature, gom record h?p l? thŕnh `micro-batches`, ch?y inference, vŕ tách rięng hai lo?i output:
