+
+## Model
+
+- model key: `{metadata['model_key']}`
+- model family: `{metadata['model_family']}`
+- threshold: `{metadata['threshold']}`
+- positive label: `{metadata['positive_label']}`
+- negative label: `{metadata['negative_label']}`
